main event: A witness reported observing a large, bright, elliptical object hovering and maneuvering at a low altitude over Lodi, New Jersey on April 14, 1965.
interesting points: The observation lasted approximately 11 minutes,The object was described as bright and elliptical in shape,The witness reported the object was hovering and maneuvering, The report deemed it a satellite as the conclusion,There were no photographs or physical evidence documented.
